==製作==
2020年4月，Netflix宣布將改編網路漫畫《地獄》為電視劇，並由延尚昊執導<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.khan.co.kr/view.html?art_id=202004231044001|title=연상호 감독, 웹툰 '지옥' 원작으로 넷플릭스 드라마 만든다|trans-title=Director Yeon Sang-ho makes a Netflix drama based on the webtoon'Hell'|last=Eunsung|first=Kim|date=2020-04-23|accessdate=2020-10-27|website=경향신문|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030141006/https://m.khan.co.kr/view.html?art_id=202004231044001|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月下旬，演員[[劉亞仁|劉亞仁]]、[[金賢珠|金賢珠]]、[[朴正民|朴正民]]、[[元真兒|元真兒]]、[[梁益準|梁益準]]、金信祿、[[劉慶秀|劉慶秀]]、[[李蕊_(韓國演員)|李蕊]]等人確定出演本劇<ref name="auto"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mb.com.ph/2020/08/03/train-to-busan-director-yeon-sang-ho-set-to-release-a-k-drama/|title=‘Train To Busan’ director Yeon Sang-ho set to release a K-drama|date=2020-08-02|website=Manila Bulletin|access-date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124040041/https://mb.com.ph/2020/08/03/train-to-busan-director-yeon-sang-ho-set-to-release-a-k-drama/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://annyeongoppa.com/2020/07/29/yoo-ah-in-park-jeong-min-and-more-confirmed-to-lead-the-new-netflix-supernatural-series-hellbound/|title=Yoo Ah In, Park Jeong Min, and more confirmed to lead the new Netflix supernatural series “Hellbound”|date=2020-07-29|website=Annyeong Oppa|accessdate=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030174432/https://annyeongoppa.com/2020/07/29/yoo-ah-in-park-jeong-min-and-more-confirmed-to-lead-the-new-netflix-supernatural-series-hellbound/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

